manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: GNC Mega Men Sport Not all multivitamins are created equal. GNC Mega Men Sport contains more antioxidant power than ever and over 30 clinically studied ingredients in every formula—all in smaller, easier-to-swallow pills. Key Ingredients GNC Mega Men Sport are time-released caplets that feature ingredients focused on Performance – Features beta-alanine, a high-efficiency muscle pH buffer, and carnitine, which helps use fatty acids as energy*Muscle Function – Features branched chain amino acids (BCAA) to fuel muscles and supports muscles by providing essential electrolytes that may be lost during intense exerciseAntioxidants – Packed with antioxidants to help fight free radicals that can be produced during your workout* How To Use As a dietary supplement, take two caplets daily with food.

Proven Benefits in a High-Potency Formula Step up your performance game with our best in class formula for men. In a clinical study GNC Mega Men was proven to work better than a basic multi at increasing levels of several nutrients in the body^*. Proven to Increase Levels of Key Vitamins and Nutrients^^* GNC Mega Men improved the levels of select B vitamins in the body by over 100% compared to a basic multivitamin and improved the absorption of selenium, beta carotene, and lutein by over 20% compared to a placebo^^. Proven to Help You Feel Better Our multivitamins do more than help you nail your nutritional needs — they also support mental wellbeing^*. In a clinical study, GNC Mega Men users reported feeling better^*.

Living mighty. Living long. Living fit. Every person has a different definition of what it means to live well — and at GNC— we see that as something worth celebrating. Whether you’re just getting started, or you need to keep going, GNC is committed to sparking your motivation and supporting your desire to live well. Statistical improvements in SF-36 Vitality and Mental Health scores were also observed compared to placebo. ^^ In a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study of 111 healthy participants (n=50 men), those taking the GNC vitamin and mineral blend for six weeks had statistically significant increases in serum levels of a group of B vitamins and a group of antioxidants and carotenoids, as well as SF-36 mental health scores based on a multivariate statistical analysis. reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Recommend - easy to add to your daily routine
reviews.reviewText: I've been using the GNC Mega Men Sport Daily Multivitamin for a few weeks now, and it's been a game-changer. The 180-count bottle provides a lasting supply, and I've noticed a significant boost in energy levels during workouts. The blend of vitamins and minerals tailored for active lifestyles is impressive, supporting muscle function and overall well-being. The tablet size is manageable, and it's become a seamless addition to my daily routine. While it's a bit pricier, the quality and benefits make it a worthwhile investment for anyone serious about their fitness journey. Highly recommended!
